---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Campus Tech"
  description="How Campus Tech collects, uses, and protects your data. Read our privacy policy."
>
  <div class="container privacy-wrap">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose privacy-prose">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Campus Tech ("we", "us", or "our") operates campustech.review. This page informs you of our
        policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our site.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Campus Tech is a static content site. We do not run our own servers or databases, and we do
        not directly collect personal information beyond what is submitted through our contact form.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — If you submit a message via our contact form, your name, email address, and message are collected and processed by Netlify Forms. We use this information only to respond to your inquiry.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics</strong> — We may use privacy-respecting analytics tools to understand aggregate traffic patterns (page views, referral sources). We do not use advertising-based trackers or build individual user profiles.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — Our site itself does not set cookies. Third-party services (such as Amazon, via affiliate links you click) may set their own cookies subject to their privacy policies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Campus Tech participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program and similar affiliate
        advertising programs. When you click an affiliate link on our site and make a purchase, we earn
        a small commission at no additional cost to you. Amazon and other retailers may collect data
        about your visit and purchase in accordance with their own privacy policies.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our affiliate relationships never influence our editorial opinions or product recommendations.
        We only recommend products we have tested and believe are genuinely good value.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — Hosts this website and processes contact form submissions. <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Netlify Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — Serves the Inter typeface used on this site. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Amazon</strong> — Processes purchases made through our affiliate links. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Amazon Privacy Notice</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our site is not directed at children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect
        personal information from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        If you have submitted a contact form message and wish to have that data deleted, or if you
        have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at the address on our
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page
        with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the
        updated policy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-wrap {
    padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 4rem;
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .privacy-prose h2 { margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .privacy-prose ul { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.5rem; }
  .privacy-prose li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
</style>
